 (COMM) 2 Cryptographic and Data program, High Frequency (HF) Modernization and MAF Connectivity programs. These efforts are necessary to modernize C/KC-135 to support warfighter connectivity and
 ensure the system meets all aerial refueling requirements through 2050.




